Enum MerchantManager.MerchantErrors

Enclosing interface:
MerchantManager
public static enum MerchantManager.MerchantErrors
extends java.lang.Enum<MerchantManager.MerchantErrors>

This enum consists of all the different error types that would be returned by the SDK through the response handlers while invoking the merchant manager APIs.
